{
  "stem": "27509.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And you lived-- the-- the-- the-- the population was predominantly agrarian, illiterate, poor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They couldn't afford if-- if a-- if a peasant bought himself a coat, it had to last him for a lifetime.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "If he had a pair of shoes, he didn't put it on on Sunday to go to church from the village.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He used to carry it on his shoulders.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he came to the church precinct.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there, before he entered the church, he put on the shoes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Never mind the socks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He didn't have socks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He had a bit of cloth to put around his-- his feet and then put on the shoes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the minute he came out of the church, he took off his shoes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And there were parts of Poland where the peasants had to divide a match in two because he couldn't afford to waste the whole match in one go.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So, so poor were the population.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And what sort of a potential such poverty had for an economy of a country of 33 million people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in this respect, Bialystok was a very wealthy [INAUDIBLE] because although it served the local market, but it also traded with overseas.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It exported its early products as far away as the Far East, as far away as [NON-ENGLISH] and [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I, in my travels, I came across it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- so we-- Bialystok used to import goods from the West as whole material.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because we also did not use a fine wool as we know it in-- in Australia, a sheep's wool in the first place, a rolled wool for manufacture-- they used second-hand wool.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used old cloth that they used the-- the old socks and old wooden cloth, they used to bring, sort, and then tear it to shreds again.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
